Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_cell_stack_area(25.10)                    report_cell_stack_area(25.10)

Name
       report_cell_stack_area  -  Reports  the  cell stack area definition for
       cells

Syntax
       report_cell_stack_area

       [-help]

       [-cell <cell_name>]

       [-file <file_name>]

       [-group <group_name>]

       Reports the cell stack area definition for cells.

Parameters
       -cell <cell_name>
              Specifies the cell(s) for which the cell stack  area  definition
              needs to be reported.

       -file <file_name>
              Specifies  the  file  name  in which the reported information is
              saved.

              By  default,  all  cell  stack  groups  are  reported   to   the
              cell_stack_area.rpt file.

       -group <group_name>
              Specifies  the group(s) for which the cell stack area definition
              needs to be reported.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each report_cell_stack_area parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_cell_stack_area

Related Information
              * specify_cell_stack_area

              * delete_cell_stack_area

